    "description": "《奇怪的RPG》是一款侧重Boss战的高难度、快节奏动作RPG游戏，个人开发完成。<br>游戏主线流程会经历超过十场非常有挑战性的Boss战。<br><br><strong>游戏特色</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>极具创意的武器<br>脑洞大开的各式武器，每种武器拥有完全不同的特殊效果，声控法杖、显卡双刀...挑战无限可能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/d51061d78a75e774053a22e8d962012d.poster.avif?t=1766644421\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/d51061d78a75e774053a22e8d962012d.webm?t=1766644421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/d51061d78a75e774053a22e8d962012d.mp4?t=1766644421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>快速反应的战斗系统<br>无论玩家处于僵直状态还是攻击后摇，都可以通过翻滚快速调整战斗位置。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/3ba00e158d40b6f1695b2368f752fc3b.poster.avif?t=1766644421\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/3ba00e158d40b6f1695b2368f752fc3b.webm?t=1766644421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/3ba00e158d40b6f1695b2368f752fc3b.mp4?t=1766644421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>高难度boss战<br>Boss一招一式都充满威胁,需要熟悉敌人的攻击规律才有机会击败它,另外切记时刻走位翻滚。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/49b06898ae5ed586be466ffa153ffaf2.poster.avif?t=1766644421\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/49b06898ae5ed586be466ffa153ffaf2.webm?t=1766644421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/49b06898ae5ed586be466ffa153ffaf2.mp4?t=1766644421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>奇妙丰富的无限世界<br>穿越到不同的世界去战斗，完成不一样的挑战，面对各种强敌，体验无限世界的冒险之旅。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/84d16fa74fcc7892fb354a3d380fc8d6.poster.avif?t=1766644421\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/84d16fa74fcc7892fb354a3d380fc8d6.webm?t=1766644421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902710/extras/84d16fa74fcc7892fb354a3d380fc8d6.mp4?t=1766644421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br><strong>关于开发者</strong><br>受到只狼和哈迪斯的影响,游戏的战斗节奏结合了哈迪斯的快速反应和只狼的高难度。<br>战斗方式主要依赖翻滚躲避敌人攻击，在敌人攻击间隙找到机会反击。",
